snippet.title: Johnny Depp v Amber Heard trial - Day 14
snippet.description:
In Day 14 of the #JohnnyDepp and #AmberHeard trial at the High Court in London we heard from Amber's sister Whitney Henriquez, Heard's acting coach Ms Sexton and Raquel Pennington.
